'''David Clennon''' (born [[May 10]], [[1940s#1943|1943]]) is an American actor best known for his portrayal of Miles Drentell in the ABC series ''thirtysomething''. He voiced [[Admiral/Legends|Admiral]] [[Conan Antonio Motti/Legends|Motti]] in the [[Star Wars (radio)|radio dramatization]] of [[Star Wars: Episode IV A New Hope|''A New Hope'']].

